  <brief_title>Combination of SAR3419 and Rituximab in Relapsed/Refractory Diffuse Large B-Cell Lymphoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open Label, Multicenter Phase II Study of Intravenous SAR3419, an Anti-CD19 Antibody-Maytansine Conjugate, in Combination With Rituximab in Patients With Relapsed or Refractory Diffuse Large B-Cell Lymphomas</official_title>
