  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion criteria:

          -  Histological diagnosis of Diffuse Large B-Cell Lymphoma (DLBCL)

          -  Relapsed or refractory after at least one standard treatment including rituximab

          -  CD19 and CD20 positive disease

        Exclusion criteria:

          -  No bi-dimensionally measurable lesion by CT scan (defined as presence of at least one
             tumor mass measuring &gt;1.5 x 1.5 cm)

          -  The above information is not intended to contain all considerations relevant to a
             patient's potential participation in a clinical trial.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
